## ğŸš€ SETUP INSTRUCTIONS

### 1. File Organization
- Place all HTML files in the root directory
- Keep `styles.css` and `script.js` in the root directory
- Create an `images/` folder for your photos

### 2. Image Replacement
Replace all `[Image placeholder]` divs with actual images:

```html
<!-- Replace this: -->
<div class="image-placeholder">[Description]</div>

<!-- With this: -->
<img src="images/your-image.jpg" alt="Description">
```

**Recommended image sizes:**
- Hero background: 1920x1080px or larger
- Service images: 800x600px
- Gallery images: 1200x800px
- Team photos: 600x600px (square)
- Shop photos: 1200x800px

### 3. Contact Form Setup (Formspree)

1. Go to [Formspree.io](https://formspree.io)
2. Sign up for a free account
3. Create a new form
4. Copy your form endpoint ID
5. In `contact.html`, replace `YOUR_FORM_ID` with your actual form ID:

```html
<form action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORM_ID" method="POST">
```

### 4. Google Maps Integration

In `contact.html`, replace the map placeholder with an actual Google Maps embed:

1. Go to [Google Maps](https://maps.google.com)
2. Search for your business address
3. Click "Share" â†’ "Embed a map"
4. Copy the iframe code
5. Replace the map placeholder div

### 5. Customization

**Update business information:**
- Company name: Search and replace "GT Autos" with your shop name
- Address: Update in footer and contact page
- Phone: Update in footer and contact page
- Email: Update in footer and contact page
- Hours: Update in footer and contact page

**Adjust colors:**
Edit the CSS variables in `styles.css`:
```css
:root {
    --color-red: #d32f2f;           /* Your primary color */
    --color-red-dark: #b71c1c;      /* Darker shade */
    --color-accent: #ff3d00;         /* Accent color */
}
```

